data.description: Price Improvement on this MODEL HOME!  This gorgeous 4 bedroom, 3 full bath home offers ample space with endless possibilities where SHORT TERM RENTALS are allowed!  As you enter the home you are greeted by stunning Italian tiles and a flex space to the right of the entrance, perfect for a at home office, gym, or play room.  Continuing through, the home opens up to a inviting living room space with a built in entertainment center, providing surround sound throughout the entire home.  One of the bedrooms and full bath are on the first level also. The combined kitchen and dining space allows for wonderful entertaining options and oversized sliding glass doors lead you out to a screened patio almost 200 square feet in size!  A FULLY FENCED back yard offers privacy and ample space, along with a papaya tree!  Heading back inside you make your way up the beautiful wood staircase to the second level were you find the Master bedroom, en-suite bath with a walk in shower, walk in closet, and double vanity.  Also on the second level is a massive loft area with a built-in, brick accent wall feature, and tons of lounging space along with a work/study station.  The additional 2 bedrooms, full bathroom, and laundry room are on the second level.  Come view this truly MOVE-IN READY home today!  Tenant willing to relocate with 30 days notice.
